title._content: Page 75 of Accounting Administration from Financial Ledger from  World's Columbian Exposition 1893

description._content:
"Installing Exhibits." heading of Page 75 of the World's Columbian Exposition Financial Ledger, which continues the accounting from page 74.

Digital Identifier: GN90799d_WCEledger_075
Original material: Digital capture from original ledger. 
Original date of object: 1892-1894
Digital file created 2003 

Select pages from the Financial Ledger on display during The Field Museum's exhibition;Opening the Vaults: Wonders of the 1893 World's Fair; October 25, 2013 - September 7, 2013.
